# This directory stores user-uploaded clothing images.
# 
# Structure:
#   uploads/
#   └── {userId}/
#       └── opt_{filename}.webp   (optimised by Sharp)
#
# - Files are served by Express at: GET /uploads/{userId}/{filename}
# - Max file size: 10MB (enforced by Multer)
# - Images are auto-resized to max 800×1000px and converted to WebP
# - This directory is listed in .gitignore — do NOT commit images
#
# Note: For production, consider using cloud storage (AWS S3, Cloudinary, etc.)
